					<description><![CDATA[<p>Aster is a next-generation decentralized exchange, as part of the Aster DeFi ecosystem, it combines order book trading with user-friendly features for both beginners and professionals. It is built as</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://ventureburn.com/what-is-aster/" data-wpel-link="internal">What Is Aster? Project, Token, Airdrop, Roadmap Explained</a> appeared first on <a href="https://ventureburn.com" data-wpel-link="internal">Ventureburn</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Aster</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"> is a next-generation decentralized exchange, as part of the<a href="https://www.asterdex.com/en" data-wpel-link="external" rel="external noopener noreferrer"> Aster DeFi</a> ecosystem, it combines order book trading with user-friendly features for both beginners and professionals. It is built as an all-in-one platform where global crypto traders can manage activity on-chain. Users can choose a simple one-click mode with MEV protection or switch to advanced tools such as stock perpetuals, grid trading, and hidden orders. The platform operates across major networks, including BNB Chain, Ethereum, Solana, and Arbitrum.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Key strengths include:</span></p>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1">Connect to the most popular blockchains easily.</li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Over $258 billion in processed trading volume</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">MEV protection to reduce front-running risks</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Yield opportunities through BNB liquid staking and the yield-bearing stablecoin USDF</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Strong community focus with airdrops and reward programs</span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">After its second <b data-path-to-node="16,1,1,0" data-index-in-node="18">Aster crypto airdrop</b>, the platform gained over 710,000 new users in one week. Trading activity rose sharply, placing it higher in DeFi rankings. Its quick response to issues like the “XPL perp glitch” further built trust. With seamless onboarding, solid infrastructure, and generous rewards, Aster is setting a strong benchmark in decentralized trading.</span></p>
<div id="attachment_193348" style="width: 1290px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-193348" class="wp-image-193348 size-full" src="https://ventureburn.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/aster1.jpg" alt="what is aster" width="1280" height="720" /><p id="caption-attachment-193348" class="wp-caption-text">Source: Asster</p></div>
<h3><b>How Aster Works         </b></h3>
<p>Aster goes beyond being a simple perpetual DEX on the BNB Chain. It&#8217;s a comprehensive derivatives platform that utilizes an order book system, offers flexible margin, and provides layered financial products through an ecosystem of interconnected core products.</p>
<h4><b>Aster Pro – Core product for Perpetual Trading</b></h4>
<p><a href="https://www.asterdex.com/en/futures/v1/BTCUSDT" data-wpel-link="external" rel="external noopener noreferrer"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Aster Pro</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> is the main product of the ecosystem. It offers perpetual trading using an order book model. Unlike platforms that depend on AMM pools, Aster Pro uses a matching engine and order book. This makes the trading experience similar to centralized exchanges while still keeping everything on-chain and transparent.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">To reduce unfair practices, Aster Pro applies systems such as the Price Index and Mark Price.</span></p>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1">The Price Index is calculated using the average price from leading spot exchanges, such as Binance, Kraken, and Huobi.</li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">The Mark Price is calculated from three parts: the price index adjusted by funding rates, the five-minute moving average, and the contract price.</span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This structure helps prevent manipulation and makes trading fairer.</span></p>
<div id="attachment_193339" style="width: 1546px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-193339" class="wp-image-193339 size-full" src="https://ventureburn.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/aster-2.jpg" alt="Aster Pro – Core product for Perpetual Trading" width="1536" height="941" /><p id="caption-attachment-193339" class="wp-caption-text">Source: Asster</p></div>
<h4><b>Aster Spot – The perfect piece for Aster</b></h4>
<p><a href="https://www.asterdex.com/en/spot/BTCUSDT" data-wpel-link="external" rel="external noopener noreferrer"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Aster Spot</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> is another important part of the ecosystem. It adds spot trading to the platform, using a central limit order book model. This makes the experience close to what users find on centralized exchanges. At the same time, it keeps the benefits of decentralization, such as transparency and self-custody of funds. Aster Spot works as a complement to the perpetual market, completing the full Aster Defi trading system.</span></p>
<h4><b>Aster Earn – Profit optimization tool for users</b></h4>
<p><a href="https://www.asterdex.com/en/earn" data-wpel-link="external" rel="external noopener noreferrer">This section</a> of the platform focuses on <b data-path-to-node="2,1" data-index-in-node="78">income generation</b>. It manages staking and <b data-path-to-node="2,1" data-index-in-node="120">interest-bearing</b> assets, while also supporting tokens that deliver <b data-path-to-node="2,1" data-index-in-node="187">consistent rewards</b>. USDF, the protocol’s native stablecoin, is the flagship product here. It is <b data-path-to-node="2,1" data-index-in-node="283">engineered</b> to provide <b data-path-to-node="2,1" data-index-in-node="305">reliable returns</b> while remaining resilient across fluctuating market conditions.</p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The main products under Aster Earn include:</span></p>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>asBNB</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">: A liquid staking token for BNB with APY up to 30%. Rewards come from sources such as Binance Launchpool, hodler airdrops, and Megadrop. Users can restake asBNB on other protocols like Binomial or Kernel DAO for extra rewards.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>asUSDF</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">: A yield-bearing token of USDF with around 3.6% APY. The yield comes from delta-neutral positions and funding fee strategies on Aster.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>asBTC</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">: A liquid staking token for Bitcoin with APY up to 5%, based on stable trading strategies.</span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">USDF itself is one of Aster’s most important products. It is backed 1:1 with USDT but has a unique feature: it generates yield. Users can deposit USDT to mint USDF at a 1:1 ratio, then stake USDF to receive asUSDF and weekly interest from Aster’s strategies.</span></p>
<div id="attachment_193340" style="width: 1393px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-193340" class="wp-image-193340" src="https://ventureburn.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/aster-3.jpg" alt="Aster Earn – Profit optimization tool for users" width="1383" height="959" /><p id="caption-attachment-193340" class="wp-caption-text">Source: Asster</p></div>
<h3><b>Aster Team</b></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Aster is the result of a merger between Astherus and </span><a href="https://www.apollox.finance/en" data-wpel-link="external" rel="external noopener noreferrer"><span style="font-weight: 400;">APX Finance</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">, two projects that already operated on BNB Chain. Together they processed more than $258 billion in volume before restructuring. The team is made up of blockchain engineers, researchers, and traders with strong experience in decentralized derivatives.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Most members keep their identities private, except for Leonard, who is known as the Aster founder. The lack of public details may be due to legal reasons, but their track record with Astherus and APX Finance gives them credibility.The success of those earlier projects shows commitment and skill, helping the community trust the <b data-path-to-node="12,1,1,0" data-index-in-node="99">Aster team crypto</b> developers.</span></p>
<h3><b>Aster Token</b></h3>
<div id="attachment_193341" style="width: 1416px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-193341" class="wp-image-193341" src="https://ventureburn.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/aster-4.jpg" alt="Aster Token" width="1406" height="791" /><p id="caption-attachment-193341" class="wp-caption-text">Source: Asster</p></div>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The ASTER token is the native asset of the ecosystem. It has a total supply of 8 billion and its Aster release date and <b data-path-to-node="20,1,1,0" data-index-in-node="67">Aster token launch date</b> were September 17, 2025. The launch created excitement in the market and attracted wide adoption.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The <b data-path-to-node="8,1,1,0" data-index-in-node="5">Aster token distribution</b> highlights the platform’s community-first strategy. More than half the supply, 53.5%, was allocated to airdrops. Other parts include 30% for ecosystem and community development, 7% for the treasury, 5% for the team, and 4.5% for liquidity.</span></p>
<p><b>ASTER Token Details:</b></p>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>Token Name</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">: Aster</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>Ticker:</b> <span style="font-weight: 400;">$ASTER</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>Token format:</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> BEP-20 on Binance Smart Chain</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>Token address</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">: 0x000Ae314E2A2172a039B26378814C252734f556A</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>Smart Contract:</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> To be announced</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>Token Type</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">: Utility</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>Total Supply:</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> 8,000,000,000 AST</span></li>
</ul>
<h3><b>Aster Fundings</b></h3>
<p>Aster’s funding history began with Astherus, which received early backing from YZI Labs, previously known as Binance Labs. This support came in late 2024 as a form of strategic financing, though the exact amount was never shared. Later, Astherus merged with APX Finance to create Aster, combining their infrastructure and large trading volume into one platform.</p>
<div id="attachment_193342" style="width: 1210px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-193342" class="wp-image-193342 size-full" src="https://ventureburn.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/aster-5.jpg" alt="Aster Fundings" width="1200" height="675" /><p id="caption-attachment-193342" class="wp-caption-text">Source: Asster</p></div>
<h3><b>Aster Roadmap</b></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The roadmap includes the creation of Aster Chain, a dedicated Layer 1 blockchain. This network is designed for high-performance derivatives trading and will use zero-knowledge proofs to protect user privacy. This expansion shows how the Aster crypto platform plans to grow beyond its exchange and strengthen its place in the Aster DeFi market.</span></p>
<h2><b>Who’s Eligible for $ASTER?</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Aster is rewarding its early supporters through airdrops. To qualify for $ASTER tokens, users need to meet one of the following:</span></p>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Earn Rh or Au points from </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Aster <a href="https://docs.asterdex.com/stage-1-spectra/aster-spectra-stage-1" data-wpel-link="external" rel="external noopener noreferrer">Spectra</a></span><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Stage 0 or Stage 1.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Receive Aster Gems allocations from community or partner events.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Trade on Aster Pro during the window from 00:00 UTC, June 23 to 23:59 UTC, August 24, 2025.</span></li>
</ul>
<p>Additionally, participants in Aster Spectra programs must reach a minimum points level to qualify.</p>
<h2><b>How To Get Aster Airdrop?</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Users have 30 days to claim their airdrop directly on Aster’s website. The team will redirect any tokens not claimed by October 17, 2025, to fund ecosystem development.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">To check eligibility and claim tokens:</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Go to the </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Aster <a href="https://www.asterdex.com/en" data-wpel-link="external" rel="external noopener noreferrer">website</a></span><span style="font-weight: 400;">, open the </span><b>“$ASTER Airdrop”</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> tab in the top menu, and click </span><b>“Claim Airdrop.”</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> You can also use the official airdrop page here:</span><a href="https://www.asterdex.com/en/airdrop" data-wpel-link="external" rel="external noopener noreferrer"> <span style="font-weight: 400;">https://www.asterdex.com/en/airdrop</span></a></p>
<div id="attachment_193344" style="width: 1320px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-193344" class="wp-image-193344 size-full" src="https://ventureburn.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/aster-7.jpg" alt="How To Get Airdrop?" width="1310" height="652" /><p id="caption-attachment-193344" class="wp-caption-text">Source: Asster</p></div>
<p>If you are wondering <b data-path-to-node="24,1,1,0" data-index-in-node="22">when is the Aster airdrop</b>, note that from September 11 at 07:00 UTC+0, you can connect your wallet to check eligibility.</p>
<div id="attachment_193343" style="width: 1546px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-193343" class="wp-image-193343 size-full" src="https://ventureburn.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/aster-6.jpg" alt="How To Get Aster Airdrop?" width="1536" height="700" /><p id="caption-attachment-193343" class="wp-caption-text">Source: Asster</p></div>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The claim window opens on September 17 at 09:00 UTC+0. Click </span><b>“Claim”</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> and confirm the transaction.</span></p>
<div id="attachment_193345" style="width: 1304px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-193345" class="wp-image-193345 size-full" src="https://ventureburn.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/aster-8.jpg" alt="How To Get Airdrop?" width="1294" height="520" /><p id="caption-attachment-193345" class="wp-caption-text">Source: Asster</p></div>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Once the claim is complete, check your balance. The tokens will appear in your Aster Spot account.</span></p>
<div id="attachment_193346" style="width: 1324px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-193346" class="wp-image-193346 size-full" src="https://ventureburn.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/aster-9.jpg" alt="How To Get Aster Airdrop?" width="1314" height="528" /><p id="caption-attachment-193346" class="wp-caption-text">Source: Asster</p></div>
<p>Always stay alert for scams. Therefore, only use the official airdrop link when claiming tokens.</p>
<div id="attachment_193347" style="width: 1288px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-193347" class="wp-image-193347 size-full" src="https://ventureburn.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/aster-10.jpg" alt="How To Get Airdrop?" width="1278" height="1242" /><p id="caption-attachment-193347" class="wp-caption-text">Source: Asster</p></div>
<h2><b>How To Withdraw Airdrop From Aster?</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">After claiming, tokens appear in your Aster spot account. You can sell them by selecting the token (e.g., $AST) and trading it for a stablecoin like USD1. Once sold, go to the </span><b>Withdraw</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> or </span><b>Transfer</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> section, choose the stablecoin, and send it to your external wallet such as Binance. Confirm the transaction, keeping in mind network gas fees may apply.</span></p>
<h2><b>What Is the Date of Aster TGE?</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Aster confirmed its token generation event (TGE) on September 17, 2025 to October 17, 2025. On that date, 704 million ASTER tokens became available to claim. </span><a href="https://www.asterdex.com/en/stage2/team" data-wpel-link="external" rel="external noopener noreferrer"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Genesis Phase 2</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> is now live and runs until October 5, 2025, at 23:59 UTC. Users can trade, hold positions, and invite others on Aster Pro to collect Rh points. These points can be used to compete for round two of the airdrops. The program explains allocation rules, steps to participate, and risks involved.</span></p>
<h2><b>Aster Airdrop: Conclusion</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Aster is becoming one of the most complete decentralized exchanges, combining perpetuals, spot trading, and yield products. Instead of targeting private investors, the project rewards active users through large airdrop programs. This strategy has driven rapid growth and adoption.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Built on the foundation of Astherus and APX Finance, the platform runs across major chains like BNB Chain, Ethereum, Solana, and Arbitrum. Moreover, its simple trading options make it beginner-friendly. Advanced tools such as hidden orders and grid trading also serve experienced traders.</span></p>
<h4><b>Advantages:</b></h4>
