<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">MEV protection for safer trading</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Multi-chain access across leading blockchains</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Strong focus on community growth through token rewards</span></li>
</ul>
<h4 data-start="133" data-end="153"><strong data-start="133" data-end="151">Disadvantages:</strong></h4>
