					<description><![CDATA[<p>What Is Kalshi? Kalshi is a regulated prediction market where users can trade event outcomes just like financial assets. It’s not a casino or gambling platform. Kalshi works under U.S.</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://ventureburn.com/what-is-kalshi/" data-wpel-link="internal">What Is Kalshi? Project, Token, Airdrop, Roadmap Explained</a> appeared first on <a href="https://ventureburn.com" data-wpel-link="internal">Ventureburn</a>.</p>
